c: 48
v: 6
t: "Aur un munafiq mardon aur auraton aur mushrik mardon aur auraton ko saza de jo Allah ke mutaliq burey gumaan rakhte hain. Burayi ke phair mein woh khud hi aa gaye hain, Allah ka gazab unpar hua aur usne unpar laanat ki aur unke liye jahannum muhayya kardi jo bahut hi bura thikana hai"